reviewText: Video was of good quality and the ladies were very attractive and the exercises were easy to follow. This video will get you up and moving and feeling better as you follow along with these lovely ladies.

The video is "OK," but the title is a lie. It is not a TOTALLY Nude Warm-Up & Stretch. Of the nine, attractive hard bodies in this video, two of them  insist on wearing something every time they are on camera--Tatum Pierce is ALWAYS wearing socks and a black sports bra, Rebecca Blue is ALWAYS wearing black short shorts. Why? They are both porn stars, but insist on being covered (partially) for this video. It looks stupid!
This is NOT an instructional video by any stretch of the imagination (pun intended); at least six of the women are porn stars, not workout gurus. The camera work is marginal much of the time. This video is strictly eye candy and nothing else!
Ordered three items and received them within a couple days. I opened up the package still wrapped in plastic and no dvd was inside.
I rather enjoyed their fun exercises and smiles while they worked it like a woman having a girls night out. Plenty of skin and good times.
Love Karlie but the DVD was a waste of time. To much nothing and not enough of the creamy center. I didn't get this one because I need to excercise..so unless you do need to...stay away and jog.
Some sellers would have you believe its 2 videos but its not the warm up and stretch are all in same video..Nice models but not enough close ups where you would expect out of this type video.

Totally Nude Warm-Up & Stretch is fifty-five minutes long and was released on March 8, 2010. Most of the ladies in this video are porn stars and not professional instructors. The first six minutes of the video is the introduction of the ladies and after that the routine begins. With the exception of Tatum Pierce and Rebecca Blue, all the other ladies are totally nude. Tatum and Rebecca work out together on the DVD and Tatum wears black and pink socks and a black work-out bra and not shorts. Rebecca on the other hand wears black short shorts and nothing else. The video is hard to follow along to and there is no instruction. Only the ones that I put an asterisk next to are the ones that I felt a person could follow along to. There is no oral instruction what so ever and at times you would need some work-out props. Also not included in the DVD is a Scene Selection menu; so if you wanted to try some of the stretches and not watch the whole video. One other thing to note is the camera operator. The person operating the camera was not that great. A third of the workouts were close-up of the ladies and that made it impossible to see the workout. So unless your idea of a work-out is to sweat watching nude ladies warm-up and stretch, then go ahead and buy. Totally Nude Warm-Up & Stretch gets a D.

Totally Nude Pilates Workout is fifty-five minutes and is included with the Totally Nude Warm-Up & Stretch DVD. Totally Nude Pilates Workout includes four of the ladies from Totally Nude Warm-Up & Stretch DVD. Totally Nude Pilates Workout is totally useless. For a good forty-five minutes of the DVD you will need a Pilates Exercise Machine and if you don't own then you are going have to go out and buy one. Only about ten minutes was a mat workout. The camera operator did better job this time around then that person did in Totally Nude Warm-Up & Stretch. This is an entertainment only DVD.

Fun follows function. I live in a "high rise" apartment and I am up in age. So I exercise in my apartment and this fit the bill. The pace was my speed and not complicated. AND trainers made it exciting.

Sounds like an erotic concept, but it is so poorly done that it's not entertaining at all.
Lighting:  Horrible
Camerawork:  Horrible
Music:  Horrible

To be honest, I only watched about half-way through and couldn't take it any more.  I feel like I wasted the money and time I spent on this.
But the girls are not all completely naked.
A definite must for your film library . I have watched it 75 times and if you ever want to become a cheerleader this could be for you !
